        "$:/plugins/.mr/slider/slider-contents": {
            "text": "@@color:red; Slider version: {{$:/plugins/.mr/slider/slider-contents!!version}}@@\n\nThe ''slider'' {{$:/plugins/.mr/slider/readme!!version}} plugin consists of the following tiddlers:\n<div style=\"background-color:#ffffaa;font-size:0.75rem;font-color:red;font-weight:300;padding-left:10px;margin-top:10px;\">\n$:/plugins/.mr/slider/manager/slider-list<br> may need be corrected in TW 5.1.18 for ''exclude'' atribute.\n</div>\n\n<ol style=\"background-color:#eee;padding:12px 36px;\"> \n  <$list filter=\"[all[shadows+tiddlers]search:title[$:/plugins/.mr/slider]sort[title]] [search:title[$:/plugins/.mr/slider]]\" variable=\"myTid\">\n    <li>\n      <$link to=<<myTid>> >\n        <$set name=\"listItem\" value={{{ [<myTid>removeprefix[$:/plugins/.mr/slider/]] }}} emptyValue=<<myTid>> >\n          <$text text=<<listItem>>/>\n        </$set>\n      </$link>\n    </li>\n  </$list>\n</ol>\n\n---\nTo edit: [[$:/plugins/.mr/slider/slider-contents]]",
